OL,3,C'Sleepless nights' for residents
OL,4,Cunable to return home because of
OL,5,Cunsafe flats
OL,7,FSam Blackledge reports on deepening
OL,8,Ffrustration due to an unstable
OL,9,Fbuilding in Plymouth
OL,11,FPeople who were forced to leave their
OL,12,Fhomes because of an 'unsafe' block of
OL,13,Fflats in Plymouth say they are
OL,14,Fsuffering "sleepless nights" because
OL,15,Fof their ordeal.
OL,17,FThe city council says work is ongoing
OL,18,Fto assess and stabilise Evolution Cove
OL,19,Fin Stonehouse, which is at risk of
OL,20,Fcollapse.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776888354
OL,3,C'Sleepless nights' for residents
OL,4,Cunable to return home because of
OL,5,Cunsafe flats
OL,7,FRoad closures could last until the end
OL,8,Fof May, and it is still not clear how
OL,9,Flong people will be stuck in temporary
OL,10,Faccommodation.
OL,12,FMorgan Rees and his wife Libby were
OL,13,Fforced to leave their flat in Emma
OL,14,FPlace Ope, opposite Evolution Cove, on
OL,15,FFriday evening as the council and fire
OL,16,Fservice issued a 'prohibition notice'
OL,17,Fand set up a cordon around the area.
OL,19,FThey are currently staying at a family
OL,20,Fmember's house and waiting for updates.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776888354
OL,3,C'Sleepless nights' for residents
OL,4,Cunable to return home because of
OL,5,Cunsafe flats
OL,7,F"We've been told nothing," Morgan told
OL,8,FITV News.
OL,10,F"We haven't been told why we've been
OL,11,Fevacuated, we've had to piece that
OL,12,Ftogether ourselves, we haven't been
OL,13,Ftold how long we're going to be out
OL,14,Ffor, when we're going to be allowed
OL,15,Fback in.
OL,17,F"I have read online that we were
OL,18,Fadvised to leave and we had the option
OL,19,Fto stay, which isn't the case at all.
OL,20,FMy wife was told get everything you
OL,21,Fcan and get out basically.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776888354
OL,3,C'Sleepless nights' for residents
OL,4,Cunable to return home because of
OL,5,Cunsafe flats
OL,7,F"The stress and anxiety is a lot for
OL,8,Fmyself and my wife at the minute.
OL,9,FSleepless nights and worrying about
OL,10,Fwhen I'm actually going to have a home
OL,11,Fagain."
OL,13,F'We've seen a massive decline in
OL,14,Ffootfall'
OL,16,FPlymouth City Council says it has
OL,17,Fcontacted people who left their homes
OL,18,Fon Friday to provide support and
OL,19,Freassurance.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776888354
OL,3,C'Sleepless nights' for residents
OL,4,Cunable to return home because of
OL,5,Cunsafe flats
OL,7,FThe council says everyone affected has
OL,8,Fbeen provided with temporary
OL,9,Faccommodation for as long as they need
OL,10,Fit.
OL,12,FMeanwhile, roads around Evolution Cove
OL,13,Fremain closed and drivers are being
OL,14,Fdiverted in and out of Royal William
OL,15,FYard.
OL,17,FBusinesses say it is having an impact
OL,18,Fon their trade.
OL,20,FRyan and Tanya Marsland run The Fig
OL,21,FTree @ 36 bistro in Admiralty Street.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776888354
OL,3,C'Sleepless nights' for residents
OL,4,Cunable to return home because of
OL,5,Cunsafe flats
OL,7,FRyan said: "On Saturday we saw a
OL,8,Fmassive decline in footfall, revenue
OL,9,Ffor the day was about 50 per cent
OL,10,Fdown, which is very unusual, and we
OL,11,Fnoticed the yard was quite a lot
OL,12,Fquieter when we went down there on
OL,13,FSunday."
OL,15,FTanya added: "It just feels like
OL,16,Fanother hurdle we've got to jump over,
OL,17,Fanother hurdle to fight, but we hope
OL,18,Fpeople will still come down, support
OL,19,Fall the local businesses in the area.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776888354
OL,3,C'Sleepless nights' for residents
OL,4,Cunable to return home because of
OL,5,Cunsafe flats
OL,7,F"We really want some support just to
OL,8,Fshow that we are here, we are open, we
OL,9,Fhaven't been told to close."
OL,11,F'Serious safety concerns'
OL,13,FThis is a saga which has now been
OL,14,Fgoing on for some time.
OL,16,FBack in December last year,
OL,17,F'structural cracking' was first
OL,18,Fdiscovered in the car park beneath
OL,19,FEvolution Cove. At the time, it was
OL,20,Fdecided that an evacuation was not
OL,21,Fnecessary.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776888354
OL,3,C'Sleepless nights' for residents
OL,4,Cunable to return home because of
OL,5,Cunsafe flats
OL,7,FOn the evening of March 20, new
OL,8,Finformation emerged and residents of
OL,9,Fthe 64 apartments were all told to
OL,10,Fleave immediately as the building was
OL,11,F'unstable' and at risk of collapse.
OL,13,FFriday April 17 brought a further
OL,14,Fupdate - an exclusion zone around the
OL,15,Fbuilding, and a legal ban on anyone
OL,16,Fentering, which the council said was
OL,17,Fdue to 'serious safety concerns'.
OL,19,F'We had to act quickly'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776888354
OL,3,C'Sleepless nights' for residents
OL,4,Cunable to return home because of
OL,5,Cunsafe flats
OL,7,FA Plymouth City Council spokesman
OL,8,Fsaid: "The council and partner
OL,9,Fagencies had to carefully assess the
OL,10,Frisks to people living, working and
OL,11,Ftravelling in the area, on foot and by
OL,12,Fcar.
OL,14,F"As there were no assurances at that
OL,15,Ftime that the building would not
OL,16,Fcollapse, the prohibition notice meant
OL,17,Fwe had to escalate our response and
OL,18,Fintroduce additional safety measures,
OL,19,Fincluding road closures.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776888354
OL,3,C'Sleepless nights' for residents
OL,4,Cunable to return home because of
OL,5,Cunsafe flats
OL,7,F"Our priority has been, and remains,
OL,8,Fthe safety of local people. We
OL,9,Fappreciate that some people feel
OL,10,Fcommunication could have reached
OL,11,Ffurther. This situation developed very
OL,12,Fquickly and we had to act at pace to
OL,13,Freduce risk.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776888354
OL,3,C'Sleepless nights' for residents
OL,4,Cunable to return home because of
OL,5,Cunsafe flats
OL,7,F"Information was shared online, on
OL,8,Fsocial media, through ward
OL,9,Fcouncillors, via local media, and
OL,10,Fthrough community groups and
OL,11,Forganisations. We recognise that not
OL,12,Feveryone will have seen those messages
OL,13,Fand we are committed to continuing to
OL,14,Fimprove how we communicate."
OL,16,FThe council says residents are
OL,17,Fexpected to be able to return home,
OL,18,Fand the road closures lifted, by the
OL,19,Fend of May.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776888354
OL,3,C'Sleepless nights' for residents
OL,4,Cunable to return home because of
OL,5,Cunsafe flats
OL,7,FA spokesman for Grey GR, the owner of
OL,8,FEvolution Cove, said: "Resident
OL,9,Fwellbeing is a key priority for Grey
OL,10,FGR. Should the remediation time take
OL,11,Flonger than expected, the alternative
OL,12,Faccommodation that Grey GR has already
OL,13,Fprovided will be extended.
OL,15,F"The safety of residents is of utmost
OL,16,Fimportance to us. Monitoring equipment
OL,17,Fhas been installed in the building.
OL,18,FData so far show building movement has
OL,19,Fbeen within tolerance levels.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1776888354
OL,3,C'Sleepless nights' for residents
OL,4,Cunable to return home because of
OL,5,Cunsafe flats
OL,7,F"A ground survey has been completed,
OL,8,Fand the findings are being used to
OL,9,Fdevelop backpropping designs. Once
OL,10,Fthese designs are finalised, the
OL,11,Fpropping works will commence.
OL,13,F"Once the work is complete and the
OL,14,Fbuilding has been confirmed as safe by
OL,15,Fsurveyors, further investigations to
OL,16,Festablish the cause of the cracking
OL,17,Fwill be undertaken."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
